 - `defensiveIterationRecordSchema`
 - `defensivePrioritizationSchema`
 - `prioritizeDefensiveAction`
+- `defensiveExecutionRequestSchema`
+- `executeDefensiveIteration`
 - `defensiveFailureStateSchema`
